arStrings.szText: “Why do you want to stop Lilith?”
I like the world the way it was--without Lilith. Her little game of rebellion will only lead to chaos. You’ve already seen visions of the damage she can do.
Yes. I know you were fed her blood. Do you feel it changing you? Perhaps not yet, but as long as Lilith walks in your world, it is only a matter of time.
